I"ù<h1 id="named-routes">named routes</h1>

<p>the code <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">match '/about'</code> automatically creates <em>named routes</em> for use in the controllers and views:</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>about_path =&gt; '/about'
about_url =&gt; 'http://localhost:3000/about'
</code></pre></div></div>
